A dizzying array of bottles, perfect for a thirst adventurer.
Maybe someone left some goodies in here ??

You cannot place any bags or containers with any items in them or you will lose the items and possibly the bag / container itself.

Do not put gold in this chest, use the bank!  (Or you will lose the gold!)

It is impossible to steal from this chest, and any of your characters can access the items from this container that you have placed in it.
With its bucket head and straw-filled chest, the combat dummy seems far from threatening.
The marble is smooth and cool to the touch. This pool is where important items that have been lost appear.
The bones of its last occupant still call it home. Are you REALLY SURE you want to sit in it ?  This is the throne of the Deathmaster EviloldSchool
